filtered_dates: SELECT d_date_sk, d_year FROM date_dim WHERE d_moy = 11
filtered_items: SELECT i_item_sk, i_brand_id, i_brand FROM item WHERE i_manufact_id = 816
main_query: SELECT dt.d_year, item.i_brand_id AS brand_id, item.i_brand AS brand, SUM(ss_sales_price) AS sum_agg FROM filtered_dates dt JOIN store_sales ON dt.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk JOIN filtered_items item ON store_sales.ss_item_sk = item.i_item_sk GROUP BY dt.d_year, item.i_brand, item.i_brand_id ORDER BY dt.d_year, sum_agg DESC, brand_id LIMIT 100
